# Copy to apps/native-rd/.env.local — gitignored, never commit.
#
# All keys here are developer-local. Per-build env (Sentry environment,
# debug-tools flag) lives in eas.json's per-profile `env` block, not here.
#
# EXPO_PUBLIC_* vars are read at bundle time. Toggling them requires a full
# Metro restart (Ctrl+C, then `bun run ios`) — a JS reload won't pick them up.

# --- Device targets (sourced by scripts/run-ios.sh & scripts/run-android.sh) ---
# When set, `bun run ios` / `bun run android` deploy to this device by default
# instead of a simulator. Existing shell exports take precedence.
# IOS_DEVICE_ID=00008140-XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
# ANDROID_DEVICE_ID=RXXXXXXX

# --- i18n pseudo-locale (dev-only safety net) ---
# Enables pseudo-locale resolution in __DEV__ builds. See docs/i18n.md.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_I18N_PSEUDO=true

# --- i18n bake-off scripts only (NOT consumed by the app) ---
# Required for `scripts/i18n/llmGateway.ts` — the locale generation pipeline.
# Generate at https://openrouter.ai/keys
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...
